OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1780085153
OL,3,CThousands to face water supply issues
OL,4,Cover weekend
OL,6,FThousands of people in Kent are facing
OL,7,Fwater issues going into the weekend as
OL,8,FSouth East Water grapples with its
OL,9,Fsupply during the hot weather.
OL,11,FBusinesses have closed and residents
OL,12,Fhave been queuing up at water bottle
OL,13,Fstations since problems began amid the
OL,14,Fbank holiday weekend heat.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/13
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
