OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1780085153
OL,3,CThousands to face water supply issues
OL,4,Cover weekend
OL,6,FSouth East Water's incident manager
OL,7,FMatthew Dean said on Friday that 3,500
OL,8,Fcustomers in the Whitstable area will
OL,9,Fsee supply "return later today", but
OL,10,Fthat tap water is "likely to remain
OL,11,Fintermittent across the weekend for
OL,12,Fall customers in this area".
OL,14,FSome 3,500 customers in Whitstable
OL,15,Fstarted to have their water supply
OL,16,Freturned to them on Thursday evening,
OL,17,Fhe added.
OL,26,@qD@LOUqD@_O]rD@SOUtD@[O]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/13
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1780085153
OL,3,CThousands to face water supply issues
OL,4,Cover weekend
OL,6,FElsewhere, 165 customers in Cranbrook
OL,7,Fare without water because the drinking
OL,8,Fwater storage tanks for the area have
OL,9,F"reached a critical level".
OL,11,FAround 10,500 customers are
OL,12,Fexperiencing low pressure or
OL,13,Fintermittent supply in Coxheath,
OL,14,FLoose, Headcorn, Herne Bay and
OL,15,FBenenden areas.
OL,26,@qD@AOUqD@ZO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/13
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1780085153
OL,3,CThousands to face water supply issues
OL,4,Cover weekend
OL,6,FMr Dean said: "We are starting to see
OL,7,Ftap water supplies returning to some
OL,8,Fcustomers across Kent, however, some
OL,9,Fare still experiencing water supply
OL,10,Fissues as a result of incredibly high
OL,11,Fdemand during this heatwave.
OL,13,F"This means for the majority of
OL,14,Fcustomers, tap water is intermittent,
OL,15,Fwith supply coming and going
OL,16,Fthroughout the day, with no water or
OL,17,Flow pressure most frequently occurring
OL,18,Fat times of the day when demand for
OL,19,Fwater is at its highest ` in the
OL,20,Fmorning and evening."
OL,26,@nD@OOUuD@AOU|D@UO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/13
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1780085153
OL,3,CThousands to face water supply issues
OL,4,Cover weekend
OL,6,FHe said nearly 230,000 litres of water
OL,7,Fhave been delivered to vulnerable
OL,8,Fcustomers and also delivered bottled
OL,9,Fwater to settings such as care homes,
OL,10,FGP surgeries, pharmacies and dentists.
OL,12,FNearly 340,000 bottles of water have
OL,13,Falso been given out at bottled water
OL,14,Fstations across the county while
OL,15,Fofficials seek to find new locations
OL,16,Fto open more water points.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/13
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1780085153
OL,3,CThousands to face water supply issues
OL,4,Cover weekend
OL,6,FIt comes as the water company received
OL,7,Fa credit rating downgrade from one of
OL,8,Fits two agencies, Moody's Ratings, on
OL,9,FThursday, putting it in breach of its
OL,10,Foperating licence with regulator Ofwat.
OL,12,FThe firm must have two investment-
OL,13,Fgrade credit ratings as a condition of
OL,14,Fits licence, and is now in
OL,15,Fconversations with Ofwat on how to
OL,16,Freturn to compliance.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/13
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1780085153
OL,3,CThousands to face water supply issues
OL,4,Cover weekend
OL,6,FSouth East Water said the move related
OL,7,Fto "the fallout from two high-profile
OL,8,Foutages and the continued resilience
OL,9,Frisk the company faces until its
OL,10,Fmedium-to-long-term investment
OL,11,Fprogrammes are completed.
OL,13,FThousands of customers were left
OL,14,Funable to access tap water, shower or
OL,15,Fflush their toilets during the outages
OL,16,Fbetween November and January.
OL,26,@oD@DOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/13
