OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41108
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1780085153
OL,3,CThousands to face water supply issues
OL,4,Cover weekend
OL,6,FEarlier this month, South East Water's
OL,7,Fchief executive, David Hinton,
OL,8,Fannounced his plans to step down just
OL,9,Fa week after the group's chairman,
OL,10,FChris Train, quit following a scathing
OL,11,Freport by MPs, who said they had "no
OL,12,Fconfidence" in the company's
OL,13,Fleadership.
OL,26,@sD@bOUtD@KO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/13
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41109
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1780085153
OL,3,CThousands to face water supply issues
OL,4,Cover weekend
OL,6,FSouth East Water's chief financial
OL,7,Fofficer, Andrew Farmer, said: "South
OL,8,FEast Water is implementing a company-
OL,9,Fwide transformation following network
OL,10,Fincidents last year to improve our
OL,11,Foperational performance and deliver on
OL,12,Four most important priority, which is
OL,13,Fa resilient supply network for our
OL,14,Fcustomers."
OL,16,FOfwat said the downgrade reinforces
OL,17,Fits position that the financial and
OL,18,Foperational turnaround of the company
OL,19,Fis "essential".
OL,26,@oD@_OUvD@KO]{D@DOU{D@NO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G9/13
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41110
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1780085153
OL,3,CThousands to face water supply issues
OL,4,Cover weekend
OL,6,FA spokesman said: "The downgrade puts
OL,7,Fthe company in breach of its licence.
OL,9,F"We want to see South East Water
OL,10,Furgently address the root causes of
OL,11,Fits latest downgrade, and we are
OL,12,Fengaging with them on potential
OL,13,Fundertakings to secure compliance with
OL,14,Fits licence."
OL,16,FThe regulator added it was "closely
OL,17,Fmonitoring" the ongoing water supply
OL,18,Finterruptions affecting Kent customers.
OL,26,@nD@SOUqD@AOUvD@MO]xD@\OUyD@KO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G10/13
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41111
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1780085153
OL,3,CThousands to face water supply issues
OL,4,Cover weekend
OL,6,F"We have already proposed a #22
OL,7,Fmillion fine following multiple supply
OL,8,Finterruptions in Kent and Sussex
OL,9,Fbetween 2020 and 2023. The company is
OL,10,Falso subject to an ongoing
OL,11,Finvestigation into customer care
OL,12,Fduring the supply outages in late 2025
OL,13,Fand early 2026," the spokesman said.
OL,15,FIn the current outage, South East
OL,16,FWater's Mr Dean continued to ask
OL,17,Fcustomers to use water for essential
OL,18,Fuses only, such as drinking, washing
OL,19,Fand cooking.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@PO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G11/13
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41112
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1780085153
OL,3,CThousands to face water supply issues
OL,4,Cover weekend
OL,6,F"We are sorry to customers who have
OL,7,Fhad interruptions or low pressure in
OL,8,Ftheir water supply and know how
OL,9,Ffrustrating it is, especially in very
OL,10,Fhot weather," he said.
OL,12,F"We will continue to do all we can to
OL,13,Fprevent and resolve the issues."
OL,15,FSome 619 million litres of water were
OL,16,Fpumped to customers on Thursday, Mr
OL,17,FDean said, which is higher than
OL,18,Faverage for this time of year.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@MO]tD@AOUuD@`O]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G12/13
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
